WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.040 --> 00:00:04.750
RACHEL O'MEARA: Thanks for
coming today to our talk

00:00:04.750 --> 00:00:05.740
at Google.

00:00:05.740 --> 00:00:07.190
I'm Rachel O'Meara,
and I'm based

00:00:07.190 --> 00:00:09.440
in San Francisco at Google.

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:13.120
I'm really excited today to
bring in Karen Henson Jones.

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:17.420
Karen is here to talk today
about her spiritual experience

00:00:17.420 --> 00:00:19.674
and journey with a
near-death experience.

00:00:19.674 --> 00:00:21.840
And I'm really interested
to hear some of the things

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:23.870
that she's going to
share with us today.

00:00:23.870 --> 00:00:27.260
She has a lot of, in her
book, "Heart of Miracles,"

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:30.500
data and scientific
evidence that she provides

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:35.120
as well from the community and
doctors and others who have now

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.430
supporting evidence that
there's a lot more information

00:00:37.430 --> 00:00:42.460
about near-death experiences
that many people now

00:00:42.460 --> 00:00:44.100
have come forward to share.

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:47.370
So Karen is here from Virginia.

00:00:47.370 --> 00:00:51.500
And she is a graduate of Cornell
in the London Business School.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:54.600
So I'm very excited
to host Karen today.

00:00:54.600 --> 00:00:56.976
And we'll host and
have her speak.

00:00:56.976 --> 00:00:58.600
We have a short video
in the beginning.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:02.428
And also, we'll have
question time at the end.

00:01:02.428 --> 00:01:03.094
